      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "The Long View\nEpisode: The Role of Solar Energy in the Near Future\nHost: Alex Morgan\nGuest: Dr."
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:1c6e27c443d1abc5",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Rafael Mendes\n\nAlex Morgan: Today we\u2019re talking about solar energy: what it can realistically do in the next 10\u201320 years, and what has to change around it."
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:6c71b8dd72f6a0f1",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Alex Morgan: People often talk about solar energy as if it\u2019s one thing, but it\u2019s really a bundle of trade-offs."
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:16227549ade3f1cb",
      "properties": {
        "speaker": "Speaker 1",
        "text": "Rafael Mendes: Yes, and it helps to name the hidden assumptions people bring into the conversation."
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:91eb700de8d2964e",
      "properties": {
        "speaker": "Speaker 1",
        "text": "Alex Morgan: What\u2019s the common misconception you see in the public debate?"
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:cdd83e3eb7ba727f",
      "properties": {
        "speaker": "Speaker 1",
        "text": "Rafael Mendes: We should distinguish between first-order impacts and second-order effects, because the second-order effects tend to dominate over time."
      },
      "type": "Quote"
    }
  ],
